Package: PlantCare3
Title: Personalized Plant Care Advice
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sabina", "Ministeru", , "sabina.ministeru@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           )
Description: PlantCare.R provides personalized care advice for 11 common houseplants. The user answers some questions in an interactive interface, and then received advice. The advice is based on the species and current stae of the plant. The information is taken from https://plantsage.org/. The user is assumed to be close to their plant. 
